---
title: Teriyaki Tofu Bowls with Stir-Fried Veggies and Garlic Sesame Rice
description: This dish brings the flavour with sesame-studded rice, teriyaki-soy-glazed tofu and a wok full of carrots, broccoli and cabbage. Every bite is packed with flavour and texture – perfect for any day of the week!
